{"id":"322279087_Yager_Index_and_Ranking_for_Interval_Type-2_Fuzzy_Numbers","abstract":"This paper presents a ranking method, two distances, and some definitions about ordering of Interval Type-2 fuzzy numbers based on the Yager index for Type-1 fuzzy sets. The proposed Yager index provides a closed form of the central tendency of well-defined Interval Type-2 fuzzy numbers. Some numerical examples are given, a comparison to the centroid of an Interval Type-2 fuzzy number is performed, and some interpretation issues are discussed.","authors":["Juan Carlos Figueroa Garcia","Y. Chalco-Cano","Heriberto Roman-Flores"],"meta":["October 2018IEEE Transactions on Fuzzy Systems PP(99):1-1","DOI:10.1109/TFUZZ.2017.2788884"],"references":["258390228_A_Proposal_to_Speed_up_the_Computation_of_the_Centroid_of_an_Interval_Type-2_Fuzzy_Set","255648529_Computing_Degrees_of_Subsethood_and_Similarity_for_Interval-Valued_Fuzzy_Sets_Fast_Algorithms","241683920_Interval-valued_Fuzzy_Sets_in_Soft_Computing","224311406_Enhanced_Karnik--Mendel_Algorithms","4260540_Enhanced_Karnik-Mendel_Algorithms_for_Interval_Type-2_Fuzzy_Sets_and_Systems","3336390_Interval_Type-2_Fuzzy_Logic_Systems_Made_Simple","314666028_Ranking_interval_type_2_fuzzy_sets_using_parametric_graded_mean_integration_representation","312037450_On_Computing_the_Footprint_of_Uncertainty_of_an_Interval_Type-2_Fuzzy_Set_as_Uncertainty_Measure","308811940_A_centroid-based_approach_for_solving_linear_programming_problems_with_Interval_Type-2_Fuzzy_technological_coefficients","308811272_Ranking_type_2_fuzzy_sets_by_parametric_embedded_representation","304291832_A_New_Ranking_Approach_for_General_Interval_Type_2_Fuzzy_Sets_Using_Extended_Alpha_Cuts_Representation","304109012_Decision-making_in_a_fuzzy_environment","301687790_Type-2_Fuzzy_Alpha-cuts","286679012_On_the_computation_of_the_distance_between_Interval_Type-2_Fuzzy_numbers_using_a-cuts","286355273_Perceptual_Computing_Aiding_People_in_Making_Subjective_Judgments","277976969_